1. Patient Management

UC-1.1: Register New Patient
Actor: Receptionist
Flow: Enter patient details (name, DOB, contact, address, blood group). System validates uniqueness by phone/email, generates patient ID, inserts record into patients 
table with auto-increment primary key.


	Code->
